  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Micafungin Against Invasive Candidiasis or Candidemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Open-label, Non-comparative Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Micafungin Against Invasive Candidiasis or Candidemia (CFDA Commitment)</official_title>
